Original LJSpeech audio is in the public domain.
Generated audio is derived from LJSpeech via neural vocoder architectures:
  HiFi-GAN (Kong et al., 2020) — files in fake/ (suffix _gen.wav)

Reference:
  Frank, J. & Schönherr, L. (2021). WaveFake: A Data Set to Facilitate
  Audio DeepFake Detection. NeurIPS Datasets and Benchmarks Track.
  https://arxiv.org/abs/2111.02813
